          },
          "plain_text": "The ocean is busy and chaotic. There are whales just beyond the waves. I’m alone in a foreign sea and I feel alert. Mostly for hunting waves, of which there are a few diamonds in the rough. The water is glassy, but the swell slightly too jumbled up; I get a few that puts a smile on the face. ",
